# Personal Portfolio Website 🌐

This is a **responsive personal portfolio website** created using **pure HTML and CSS**, with no JavaScript or frameworks involved.

### 📌 Features:
- Responsive layout for desktop and mobile screens.
- Custom navigation bar.
- Animated social icons and hover effects.
- Highlighted sections with personal introduction and goals.

### 🎯 Purpose:
This project was created as a **learning experience** while following a YouTube tutorial to explore HTML and CSS deeply. It helped me understand the fundamentals of layout structuring, media queries, and CSS animations.

> ⚠️ Note: This project is built strictly for educational purposes and does not include any licensing. Credit goes to the original YouTuber for the design inspiration.

### 🔗 Deployed Link:
[View Live Portfolio](https://htmlcssbased-portfolio-website.netlify.app/)

